{% from "components/buttons.njk" import startButton %}
{% from "components/content-box/macro.njk" import contentBox %}
{% from "components/form-header/macro.njk" import formHeader with context %}

{% extends "layouts/main.njk" %}

{% block content %}
    <main role="main" id="content">
        {% call contentBox() %}
            {{ formHeader(
                title = title,
                suffix = copy.description | safe
            ) }}

            <div class="message" role="alert">
                <p class="t3">We're moving to a new online form to tell us about your ideas - from Wednesday 20 November</p>
                <p>Our new online form makes it easier for you to tell us about your funding proposals - if you're looking for more than £10,000 from us. It launches at 11:00am on 20 November.</p>
            </div>
            
            <h2>Find out how we can help you</h2>
            <p>
                You can apply for over £10,000 to support communities to take action
                on the issues that matter to them. Once you submit your idea a local
                funding officer will aim to contact you within fifteen working days
                to seek further information or to update you on your idea’s progress.
            </p>

            {{ startButton(startUrl) }}

            <h2>Before you start</h2>
            <h3>We can fund</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Ideas taking place in England</li>
                <li>Voluntary and community sector organisations and registered charities</li>
                <li>Public bodies such as local authorities, schools and health agencies</li>
                <li>Community interest companies so long as profits are reinvested into the organisation to create more impact</li>
                <li>A group of organisations working together led by one of the organisations above</li>
                <li>Community interest companies with two or more directors (see below for ineligible CICs)</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>We can’t fund</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Ideas taking place outside of England and organisations based outside of the UK</li>
                <li>Organisations that are aimed at generating profits primarily for private distribution. Those not asset locked or organisations that can pay profits (including some CICs limited by shares) to directors or shareholders</li>
                <li>Individuals and sole traders</li>
                <li>Anyone who is applying on behalf of another organisation</li>
                <li>Organisations without at least two unconnected people on the board or committee.</li>
            </ul>

            <p><a href="{{ localify('/funding/programmes') }}">Browse all of our funding programmes</a></p>

            <h3>You'll need</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>To briefly explain your idea and why it’ll make a difference</li>
                <li>The legal name of your organisation and other organisations you may be working with</li>
                <li>Your contact details</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Other ways to apply</h2>
            <p>
                We’re available Monday–Friday from 9am to 5pm to answer questions about applying.
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Telephone</strong>: 0345 4 10 20 30</li>
                <li><strong>Textphone</strong>: 18001 plus 0345 4 10 20 30 (for those with a hearing or speech impairment)</li>
            </ul>
        {% endcall %}
    </main>
{% endblock %}
